overrungl.nfd.NFDEnumerator
All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable, Iterable<String>, Addressable
public final class NFDEnumerator extends Struct implements Iterable<String>, AutoCloseable
NFDEnumerator relies on preview features of the Java platform:
  • NFDEnumerator refers to one or more preview APIs: MemorySegment, SegmentAllocator, StructLayout.
Programs can only use NFDEnumerator when preview features are enabled.
Preview features may be removed in a future release, or upgraded to permanent features of the Java platform.
A wrapper of NFD path set enumerator.
